---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About | VTech App"
	description="VTech App is an independent free software provider focused on useful system utilities for real-world users and administrators."
>
	<header class="page-heading">
		<p class="eyebrow">About VTech App</p>
		<h1>Independent free software for practical system work.</h1>
		<p>
			VTech App is an independent free software provider focused on useful, simple, reliable
			system utilities for real-world users, technicians, and administrators.
		</p>
	</header>

	<section class="two-column">
		<article class="card">
			<h2>First focus: Windows tools</h2>
			<p>
				The first releases focus on Windows utilities for storage analysis, file copy workflows,
				and permission auditing.
			</p>
		</article>
		<article class="card">
			<h2>Linux tools are planned</h2>
			<p>
				Linux utilities are part of the future roadmap, but the catalog will only list real
				projects when they are ready.
			</p>
		</article>
	</section>

	<section class="notice">
		<h2>Project goal</h2>
		<p>
			The goal is to build software that solves practical problems without unnecessary accounts,
			lock-in, or paid-service dependencies.
		</p>
	</section>
</Layout>
